<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />May Yahweh help you in the day of trouble;</para>

<para style="q1">may the name of the God of Jacob protect you</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />and send help from the holy place</para>

<para style="q1">to support you from Zion.</para>
